Login issues

## User issue
The user can not log in.

## Possible causes
- Incorrect username or wrong password
- Temporary server issue
- Incomplete or incorrect registration
- Session or browser cache issue

## Troubleshooting steps
1. Ask the user to check their login details and reset their password if needed.
2. Ask the user to refresh the page and try a different browser.
2. Test the authentication, database, and backend systems.
3. Collect any error messages from the user.

## User-friendly response
Please make sure you are using the correct username and password. You can use the "Forgot your password?" option to reset your password and confirm your username. 

If you still cannot log in, try refreshing the page, clearing your browser cache, or using a different browser. 

If the issue persists, please share any error messages with us so we can investigate further.

## Internal note
The issue may be related to incorrect login details, temporary server issues, or problems with authentication or the database.
